    <title>永久免费云服务器LinuxOne</title>
    <link href="/1999/12/31/%E6%B0%B8%E4%B9%85%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E4%BA%91%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8LinuxOne/"/>
    <url>/1999/12/31/%E6%B0%B8%E4%B9%85%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E4%BA%91%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%99%A8LinuxOne/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs markdown"><span class="hljs-section"># 永久免费LinuxONE服务器实战手册</span><br><br><span class="hljs-section">## 〇、必要准备</span><br>[<span class="hljs-string">LinuxONE云服务器</span>](<span class="hljs-link">https://linuxone.cloud.marist.edu/#/login</span>)  <br>[<span class="hljs-string">MobaXterm终端工具</span>](<span class="hljs-link">https://mobaxterm.mobatek.net/</span>)<br><br><span class="hljs-section">## 一、核心部署流程</span><br><br><span class="hljs-section">### 1. 安装原始版本</span><br><span class="hljs-code">```bash</span><br><span class="hljs-code">wget -O install.sh http://f.cccyun.cc/bt/install_6.0.sh &amp;&amp; bash install.sh</span><br><span class="hljs-code"># 注意！安装完成后切勿登录面板</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-解除功能限制"><a href="#2-解除功能限制" class="headerlink" title="2. 解除功能限制"></a>2. 解除功能限制</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">wget --no-check-certificate https://10g.biz/downloads/LinuxPanel.zip<br>unzip LinuxPanel.zip<br>bash /root/panel/update.sh<br><span class="hljs-built_in">rm</span> -f /www/server/panel/data/bind.pl  <span class="hljs-comment"># 关键破解步骤</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-降级稳定版本"><a href="#3-降级稳定版本" class="headerlink" title="3. 降级稳定版本"></a>3. 降级稳定版本</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">wget -O install.sh http://v7.hostcli.com/install/install-ubuntu_6.0.sh<br><span class="hljs-built_in">sudo</span> bash install.sh<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4-执行绿化脚本"><a href="#4-执行绿化脚本" class="headerlink" title="4. 执行绿化脚本"></a>4. 执行绿化脚本</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">curl http://v7.hostcli.com/install/update6.sh|bash<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="5-网络配置"><a href="#5-网络配置" class="headerlink" title="5. 网络配置"></a>5. 网络配置</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">iptables -P INPUT ACCEPT<br>iptables -P FORWARD ACCEPT<br>iptables -P OUTPUT ACCEPT<br>iptables -F<br>apt-get purge netfilter-persistent -y  <span class="hljs-comment"># 仅限Ubuntu/Debian</span><br>reboot<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="二、访问验证"><a href="#二、访问验证" class="headerlink" title="二、访问验证"></a>二、访问验证</h2><ul><li>访问地址：<code>http://服务器IP:8888</code></li><li>初始账号：<code>bt_default</code></li><li>初始密码：通过<code>/etc/init.d/bt default</code>查看</li></ul><pre><code class="hljs"></code></pre>]]></content>
    
    
    
